
Voldemort walked into the bold and loud Muggle area called "The Capitol", Nagini tailing behind him. He was led bu the so-called "Peace-Keepers" to a large room. Sitting in a large chair was President Snow.
"Thank you for comimg, Voldemort." Snow said.
"Yes, I find that your so called "Hunger Games" very intriguing." Voldemort responded.
"Yes, indeed they are." Snow said, grinning maliciously.

About an hour later, they had come to an agreement.
The Hunger Games would be changed into The Hogwarts Games.
There would be twenty-four tributes from Panem and sixteen Hogwarts tributes.

This is The Hogwarts Games
